{
  "stem": "3022.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "When he was undressing at night, at the light of the moon, I could see his shining black body.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "I never saw a black person before in my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "He had the BVDs, the white shorts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "And he went to bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And he got up in the morning before I woke up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And after he left, I got up and I checked the bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "I was sure there had to be some black stains on his sheets, that something had to come off from his shiny black body.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "About two or three days later, two of those soldiers-- he wasn't among them-- came with a truckload of food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "They worked in a transportation company.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And whatever they could organize, [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] they loaded a six-by-six truck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And they pulled it into the barn, and they unloaded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And there was C-ration, K-ration cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "Among other things, there was chocolate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "I hadn't seen chocolate in six years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was this big block of cooking chocolate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hid it for myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I ate it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was constipated for four weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't eat chocolate anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But that act of kindness was the seed of my personal relationship towards people of color.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Several days later, somebody told me, your friend Oscar came in with a company of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's in the town of [GERMAN], which is about eight kilometers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It turned out that after we buried my friend Oscar alive, he got up at night and started wandering around.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was fortunate enough to walk into the POW camp of American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the German guards knew that the end was near, and they let him in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he had pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
